===Etymology===
Greek ''[[φαινόμενον]]'', "thing appearing to view", from ''[[φαίνειν]]'', "to show".
===Noun===
'''phenomenon''' (''Plural:'' '''phenomena''')
#an [[appearance]] or [[occurrence]], usually one [[evoke|evoking]] [[curiosity]]
#a [[fact]] or [[situation]] that is [[observe]]d to exist or happen but is [[unexplainable]] or [[questionable]]
